Subject: Logs Report for some MAC workstations
Description:
Hello,
While checking on a specific MAC station that was reported to be blocking USB storage devices - I noticed that the Logs Report is showing mow events for some mac workstations. Is there any way to determine why these devices are not reporting events?
I appreciate any help.
What_We_Know__c:
the customer has some computers where the agent is not communicating with the server.
as a troubleshooting step, the customer is reinstalling the agent, which seems to work.
Solution_Comment__c: reinstalling the agent fixes the issue
